 455:Core/Src/stm32f103xx_CMSIS.c ****  *  –Э–∞ —Н—В–Њ–Љ —В–∞–є–Љ–µ—А–µ –Љ—Л –љ–∞—Б—В—А–Њ–Є–Љ Delay –Є –∞–љ–∞–ї–Њ–≥ HAL_GetTick()
 456:Core/Src/stm32f103xx_CMSIS.c ****  *  PM0056 STM32F10xxx/20xxx/21xxx/L1xxxx Cortex¬Ѓ-M3 programming manual/
